data.description: !!! Open House this Sunday Mar 3rd from 1-3 p.m. Come visit your new luxury retreat conveniently located minutes from shopping, dining, Lackland AFB, entertainment areas and desirable Northside ISD schools. The handsome brick & stone exterior with an extended front patio welcome you into the spacious, light and bright floor plan with beautiful appointments featuring wood-like tile flooring, soaring 20' ceilings, wrought iron railings, crown molding, recessed lighting and more. Flexible living spaces include a living area downstairs, a game room and loft upstairs, a dedicated office with windowed French doors, two dining areas and a guest suite with full bath located downstairs. The downstairs primary suite is split from the secondary bedrooms for ample privacy and is a true owner's retreat with bay windows, dual walk-in closets, separate vanities, tiled walk in shower and a luxurious soaking tub to help you unwind at the end of a long day. Entertaining at home is a breeze with the huge island kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, a convenient pot filler, granite counters, gas cooking, tiled backsplash and a breakfast bar large enough to seat four. The adjoining breakfast room with utility desk and spacious family room create an inviting flow to the floor plan. The extended covered patio in back offers two ceiling fans and provides the perfect spot for outdoor living. New owners will also appreciate the 3 car garage, the mud room, utility area with built in storage, a cutting edge security system, Ring security cameras, Ring doorbell, faux wood blinds throughout, gorgeous HOA amenities like a pool and park just a few minutes walk away. The best part? There are NO city taxes and $0 down USDA financing available. Owner is including Washer, Dryer, Refrigerator, water softener (owned) and reverse osmosis water filter (owned), with home as well as a 1 year home warranty. ***Owners offering Epoxy floor coating treatment in garage.*** Take the first step towards luxury living and schedule your private showing today!
